{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/GrowingDevlog/20240604_codeBlock_lineNum/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"32's Dev.log","author":"han32","siteUrl":"https://gatsby-starter-bee.netlify.com","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"HSangMi/devlog"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"han32"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"88895407-455c-5f4a-9767-8b82e92af5e8","excerpt":"라인넘버 표시하기 더 자세한 설정은 공식 문서에서 확인 가능합니다!\ngatsby-remark-prismjs 1. 플러그인 설치 prismjs 플러그인 설치, 이전 포스팅에서 설치하고 에 이미있으면 생략 2. gatsby-config에 설정  플러그인 사용 활성화 3. gatsby-browser에 기본 CSS 추가 에 기본 css 추가 3. 커스텀 CSS추가 에 커스텀 css 추가","html":"<aside>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/JaeYeopHan\">@Jbee</a> 님의 블로그 템플릿을 받아서 사용 중 인데, 코드블록 디자인에 몇가지 설정을 추가하고 싶었다.  <br/>\n1. 테마 <br/>\n2. 타이틀 <br/>\n<b>2. 라인넘버</b> <br/>\n3. 하이라이트  <br/>\n</aside>\n<h2 id=\"라인넘버-표시하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B8%EB%84%98%EB%B2%84-%ED%91%9C%EC%8B%9C%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"라인넘버 표시하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>라인넘버 표시하기</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>더 자세한 설정은 공식 문서에서 확인 가능합니다!\n<a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-remark-prismjs/\">gatsby-remark-prismjs</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"1-플러그인-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"1 플러그인 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 플러그인 설치</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>prismjs 플러그인 설치, 이전 포스팅에서 설치하고 <code class=\"language-text\">package.json</code>에 이미있으면 생략</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> gatsby-remark-prismjs prismjs</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-gatsby-config에-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-gatsby-config%EC%97%90-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"2 gatsby config에 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. gatsby-config에 설정</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code> 플러그인 사용 활성화</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">gatsby-config.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-transformer-remark</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      plugins<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n          <span class=\"token comment\">//...</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n              resolve<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-remark-prismjs</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              options<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n              inlineCodeMarker<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'%'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\">              showLineNumbers<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 라인 번호 표시 활성화</span></span>              <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          <span class=\"token comment\">//...</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-gatsby-browser에-기본-css-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-gatsby-browser%EC%97%90-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8-css-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"3 gatsby browser에 기본 css 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. gatsby-browser에 기본 CSS 추가</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-browser.js</code>에 기본 css 추가</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">gatsby-browser.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'intersection-observer'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"prismjs/themes/prism-tomorrow.css\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\"><span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"prismjs/plugins/line-numbers/prism-line-numbers.css\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-커스텀-css추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EC%BB%A4%EC%8A%A4%ED%85%80-css%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"3 커스텀 css추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 커스텀 CSS추가</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">style/code.scss</code>에 커스텀 css 추가</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">style/code.scss</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">// highlight랑 number랑 같이 쓸거라 추가한 css\n.gatsby-highlight pre[class*=\"language-\"].line-numbers</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">padding-left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2.8em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">// 정렬이 안맞아서 추가한 css\n.line-numbers .line-numbers-rows</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0em 0em 0em 0.5em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1em 0em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">border-right</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid #99999952<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"[Gatsby] Prismjs 코드블록 개선(3) Line Numer 추가하기","date":"June 04, 2024","tags":["Gatsby","React","prismjs"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/GrowingDevlog/20240604_codeBlock_lineNum/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/GrowingDevlog/20240604_codeBlock_title/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[Gatsby] Prismjs 코드블록 개선(2) 타이틀 추가하기","category":"Work & Dev/GrowingDevlog"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/GrowingDevlog/20240605_codeBlock_line_highlight/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[Gatsby] Prismjs 코드블록 개선(4) Line HighLight 추가하기","category":"Work & Dev/GrowingDevlog"}}}}}